日期或确认的平台。该项目是与<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-25-steven-spohn-ablegamers-sxsw-gaming-interview.html">AbleGamers</a>合作创建的，AbleGamers 是一个非营利组织，致力于在视频游戏市场中倡导残疾人权利，领导软件和硬件开发领域的包容性工作。 AbleGamers 与 Xbox 合作设计了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-05-17-xbox-adaptive-controller-disabilities-gamepad-microsoft-tour.html">自适应控制器</a>，并为索尼创建了<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonys-project-leonardo-ps5-peripheral-is-now-the-access-controller-105010859.html">Access 控制器</a>（该工作室即将推出的以辅助功能为中心的游戏手柄）提供了意见。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/to-at-is-a-coming-of-age-game-about-at-spoke-teenager-191135661.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/to-a-t-is-a-coming-of-age-game-about-a-t-posing-teenager-191135661.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 06687907-f937-44a7-86ce-2e5ea21cc0dd</guid><dc:creator>杰西卡·康迪特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jun 2023 19:11:35 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688066047</ingested><modified> 2023-06-29T19:14:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="1720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/00cafeb0-16b1-11ee-b55c-ad92af4d475d" width="2692"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-06/00cafeb0-16b1-11ee-b55c-ad92af4d475d" width="2692"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Uvula]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[to a T]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[to a T]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Recursive puzzle adventure game 'Cocoon' will arrive on September 29th]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>得益于出色的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/humanity-will-hit-ps-plus-when-it-arrives-on-may-16th-155831161.html"><em>人性</em></a>和令人费解的<em>取景器</em>，今年将成为益智游戏的标志性一年。另一款游戏<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cocoon-limbo-designer-xbox-pc-switch-2023-191602095.html"><em>《Cocoon》</em></a>刚刚出现在发行日历上，这<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/cocoon-is-worth-getting-excited-about-181529189.html">可能是我们本月初在夏季游戏节上看到的最令人兴奋的游戏</a>。发行商 Annapurna Interactive 在夏季展示会上透露， <em>《Cocoon》</em>将于 9 月 29 日登陆 PS4、PS5、Nintendo Switch、Xbox One、Xbox Series X/S 和 Steam。它也将在 Game Pass 上提供。</p><p>这是 Geometric Interactive 的第一个项目，该项目由 Playdead <em>（Limbo</em>和<em>Inside</em>背后的工作室）的两位前开发人员创立。 <em>Cocoon</em>是一款冒险游戏，您可以使用球体来解决谜题。当你将球体放在插槽上时，你可以跳入其中 - 每个球体都是自己的世界，具有独特的机制和需要击败的老板。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <em>Cocoon</em>就是关于递归的。您可以将球体带入另一个世界以利用其能力，例如能够看到原本看不见的路径或激活开关。你也可以选择从球体中跳出来，这将是解决一些谜题和绕过障碍的关键。我们很期待这一点。 </p><div id="c5a82876315b4e4fa1308ffb4e614ae3"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xub7_FhlWws" title="YouTube 视频播放器" allowfullscreen="" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0"></iframe></div>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/recursive-puzzle-adventure-game-cocoon-will-arrive-on-september-29th-190537652.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/recursive-puzzle-adventure-game-cocoon-will-arrive-on-septem